<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cough2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cough,</orth> vb., to make a noisy effort to throw offending matter from the lungs: <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.932" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 932</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 173</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 1, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 2, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.4.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 4, 63</bibl> <emph>(which beasts would c. at).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>